reviews.review_text:
just another good 1985 dead show had  a tape of second set always played it....
 good recording for aud well worth the download
check out the china-rider its top notch

I Was There Saw the Dead over 30 times during the 80s and into the early 90s. This was one of my all time favorites. Epic vibe that night, great sets, and it was my personal best of times. Every time I listen to it i'm right back there.
